14:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston aholisi uchun elektr energiya tariflari 6 bosqichli shkala bo'yicha belgilangan: iste'mol qancha ko'p bo'lsa, kVt·soat uchun tarif shuncha yuqori. Oyiga birinchi 200 kVt·soat eng arzon, 1 001 kVt·soatdan ortiq iste'mol — maksimal tarif bo'yicha. Bunday tizim elektr energiyani tejab iste'mol qilishga rag'batlantiradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Aholi uchun tarif setkasi (2025): 1-bosqich (0-200 kVt·soat) — 600 so'm/kVt·soat; 2-bosqich (201-500) — 800 so'm; 3-bosqich (501-1 000) — 1 000 so'm; 4-bosqich (1 001-5 000) — 1 500 so'm; 5-bosqich (5 001-10 000) — 1 750 so'm; 6-bosqich (10 000 dan ortiq) — 2 000 so'm/kVt·soat."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash misoli: oyiga 700 kVt·soat iste'mol. 1-bosqich: 200 × 600 = 120 000 so'm. 2-bosqich: 300 × 800 = 240 000 so'm. 3-bosqich: 200 × 1 000 = 200 000 so'm. Jami: 560 000 so'm. O'rtacha narx: 800 so'm/kVt·soat."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"class